Package affymetrix.fusion.chp

Class Summary
FusionBaseCallType Holds a call at a given position.
FusionCHPData A base class for all CHP data objects.
FusionCHPDataReg A class used to self register CHP data classes.
FusionCHPGenericData This class provides storage and reading capabilities for CHP files
FusionCHPGenericData.Reg A class to register a generic CHP reader.
FusionCHPHeader Stores the contents of the header of a CHP file.
FusionCHPLegacyData Provides storage for data in a GCOS CHP file.
FusionCHPLegacyData.Reg A class to register the legacy CHP reader.
FusionCHPMultiDataData This class provides storage and reading capabilities for multi-data CHP files
FusionCHPMultiDataData.Reg A class to register the multi-data CHP reader.
FusionCHPQuantificationData This class provides storage and reading capabilities for Quantification CHP files
FusionCHPQuantificationData.Reg A class to register the Quantification CHP reader.
FusionCHPQuantificationDetectionData This class provides storage and reading capabilities for quantification/detection CHP files
FusionCHPQuantificationDetectionData.Reg A class to register the Quantification CHP reader.
FusionCHPTilingData This class provides storage and reading capabilities for tiling CHP files
FusionCHPTilingData.Reg A class to register the tiling CHP reader.
FusionExpressionProbeSetResults Expression analysis probe set results for the MAS5 algorithm
FusionForceCallType A type to hold the force call, the call that the algorithm would have made if the thresholds were relaxed.
FusionGenotypeProbeSetResults Stores results for a genotyping probe set.
FusionResequencingResults Stores results for a resequencing analysis.
FusionUniversalProbeSetResults Stores results for a universal probe set.
